his time, Israel faces a more complicated, ambitious task as it tries to target a much larger, better organized and armed organization than the Black September operatives from the 1970s.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.636532831398473e-55, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a more complicated, ambitious task\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"a much larger, better organized and armed organization\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"the Black September operatives\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1970s\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the political stakes for Israel and the rest of the world are much higher.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.636532831398473e-55, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the political stakes\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barnea's comments at the funeral Jan. 3 came a day after a drone strike killed a senior Hamas leader, Saleh al-Arouri, in the Lebanese capital of Beirut.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barnea_(bivalve)\", \"score\": 0.9772269441514208, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barnea\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barnea_(bivalve)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barnea_(bivalve)\"}, {\