to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"Arouri\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This would be a remarkable achievement for any intelligence service,\\\" said Roule, now a senior adviser to United Against Nuclear Iran, a nonprofit that says it focuses on threats posed by the Islamic Republic of Iran.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a remarkable achievement\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"any intelligence service\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"Roule\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"now a senior adviser\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"United\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"Nuclear Iran\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"a nonprofit\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"threats\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"the Islamic Republic\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"Iran\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the Beirut street where Arouri was located and killed, local residents told NBC News they had no idea anyone was living in what they assumed was a derelict building.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2175, \"end\": 2181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beirut\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.613409631164242e-67, \"text\": \"Beirut\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beirut\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beirut\"}, {\"begin\": 2247, \"end\": 2255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.999293460484647, \"rank\": 0.000707039066713231, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arouri\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"local residents\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\